{"tid":1465161,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我屌你老母阿死金毛","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:43.000Z","uid":156096,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1be314c506fc048cd3b8540d96c25419964595","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講有咁多巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先條仆街仔打自己友，打救護，打立場哥哥已經9成唔係自己友。<br />\n第二，條友同身邊幾個人(唔肯定佢地識唔識)不斷咁挑起現場情緒，又話要打死個公安。<br />\n但當情緒高漲時，佢突然走人。過左無耐，黑警就黎左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果佢咁想公安死，會唔會走人阿?<br />\n第三，明明開頭大家都無衝狗車，條仆街仔突然出黎阻住，好似驚死人無衝咁。<br />\n敢問一句，佢咁勇武，9成發過夢啦，咁點會唔驚上鏡阿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee925c4695760d98dff4d9f1f2baf60e470cc0b4","tid":1465161,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6fe16f2bc539594dc638ef8a7b12fa43a5b256b","tid":1465161,"uid":48162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKkdEyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKkdEyZ.jpg&h=9027ee38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e132b24d651027678ec6557bff578c5f0cd546d1","tid":1465161,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"好多鬼搞挑釁, 而家冇辦法, 可以點控制?"},{"pid":"617093665f07487e9d6cbb87c74e2008b3f7b9cf","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee925c4695760d98dff4d9f1f2baf60e470cc0b4","tid":1465161,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"真係唔係割阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁都係割，咁我屌811班黑警卧底又係咪割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n如果條仆街唔出黎交代，場運動遲早比佢玩死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec48869c7a885eb0c05eb5703c61f35d6c3a613","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母阿死金毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d867d0a6f1daa584c104ec8526324e4d71f5ddb","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"跟本唔會有人敢單刀阻警車。<br />\n和理非唔會咁做，勇武更加唔會咁多鏡頭下上鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多次，屌你老母阿"},{"pid":"1437c1b278fa80c3c3d6df1ec2b6bc093cdbc036","tid":1465161,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa8e7a330bf6fd68b3bb2634be06268d9c437aa","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"推到條仆街仔出黎交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5de1f64219ea4fbe5db4b5b4b6715f349bd044","tid":1465161,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"無人跟金毛?"},{"pid":"cf1d7e38746d854d7da0e3e30d3afe18742b03dd","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd5de1f64219ea4fbe5db4b5b4b6715f349bd044","tid":1465161,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"無人跟金毛?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"佢圍住個公安，有手足問佢過佢野，佢話自己無打過人<br />\n我屌佢啦，真係勇武怕咩認阿?佢都企喺最前打自己友同記者啦<br />\n咁都唔係話鬼，我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192cd6ec2221c04250f71f25f2a3ccc952f5898a","tid":1465161,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快撚啲出黎交代，因為你先有手足被拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d168271aa96a7fdbefb8711775b319ffcdcb17","tid":1465161,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:43.000Z","msg":"加油搵一搵依位人士"},{"pid":"95477aad41a117681fcc0d22e87369f8a7ef1142","tid":1465161,"uid":25163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"我企正佢後面真係唔撚見佢打人喎<br />\n係我後面既又係咁講佢有打人 你地點睇到？<br />\n佢走係因為後面班人叫佢出黎佢先出架喎"}]}